Replication controller: 
=================================
Note: Pod controller like rc or rs not replicate data between pods. it only maintain containers state.

1) RC: replication controller (it's control replica value)
      1. It maintain pod state.
      2. High Avaliable
      3. Scalability

          Note: replication controller create by only file method.

root@kube-master:~# cat rc.yml
apiVersion: v1
kind: ReplicationController
metadata:
  name: con1-rc                 <<  name of rc controller
spec:
  replicas: 2
  selector:
    app: nginx                 
  template:
    metadata:
      name: nginx
      labels:
        app: nginx
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: nginx
        image: nginx
        ports:
        - containerPort: 80
