Now Topic is => Deployment controller/Application rollout and rollback?
========================================================================
Rollout => update packages on lastet version.
Rollback => rollback on previous version.

RC: works on equalty based selector.
RS: RC + set based selector.

Note: rc and rs not provide live rollout and rollback that why deployment conteroller come in pitcure.

Deployment controller: ( provide rc and rs all functionality )
  1) pod state maintain
  2) scalability
  3) Rollout and rollback

